.SH NAME
jkmeter \- Jkmeter is a horizontal or vertical bargraph audio level meter for Jack Audio Connection Kit
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B jkmeter
.RI [ options ] 
.br
.SH DESCRIPTION
This manual page documents briefly the
.B jkmeter
.PP
